// empty slice mounts everything (the canonical `./<bin> server`
// behavior). Workers and operators are always constructed;
// cmd/server.go gates which of them START using the same name set.
// Name filtering — including the unknown-name warning and the loud
// registered-vs-excluded filter banner — lives in appkit.Run.
